John Maguire, CEO of Friendly's Ice 
Cream LLC, talks about the strategy he's used in his year as CEO
to improve the fast food chain. Maguire talks with Bloomberg's 
 Tom Keene  and  Michael McKee  on Bloomberg Radio's "Bloomberg 
Surveillance."      (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 09:23
 